    {
      "id": "docs-nb:39ba6efea3",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "A .klz parcel moves work between the two: pack a project into a single\nfile (or extract loose files into one), then merge/unpack on the other side."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "En **`.klz`-pakke** flytter arbeid mellom de to: `pack` et prosjekt til én enkelt\nfil (eller `extract` løse filer til én), og deretter `merge`/`unpack` på den andre siden."
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:3bb5358381",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Common extract options"
