      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:59cfbf0f02",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "You install it once. After that you ask Claude in plain language; it decides when\nto call kapi."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Du installerer det én gang. Etter det spør du Claude i naturlig språk; den\navgjør når den skal kalle `kapi`."
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:5a59ddfa1e",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Ad-hoc or project?"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Ad hoc eller prosjekt?"
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:5bc7ae2d1c",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Project: two loops, both ending at `merge`"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Prosjekt: to sløyfer som begge ender i `merge`"
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:5bf48987eb",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Kapi Desktop Overview"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Oversikt over Kapi Desktop"
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T13:20:27Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T13:20:27Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:5d76658c6f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Generate pseudo-translations to test your UI for truncation and layout issues.\nPress ▸ Run — it seeds a small messages.json and writes messages-qps.json,\nwhich you can preview in the Files panel:"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Generer pseudooversettelser for å teste grensesnittet ditt for avkutting og\nlayoutproblemer. Trykk **▸ Run** — den oppretter en liten `messages.json` og\nskriver `messages-qps.json`, som du kan forhåndsvise i **Files**-panelet:"
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:5e2a32328c",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Input can be a file argument, --text \"…\", or piped via stdin. Rewrite off-voice\ncontent — forbidden terms, competitor mentions, jargon:"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Inndata kan være et filargument, `--text \"…\"`, eller sendes via stdin. Skriv om\ninnhold som bryter med stemmen — forbudte termer, konkurrentomtaler, sjargong:"
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:5f85f1c461",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "One XLIFF 2.2 per source → target pair under out/:"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Én XLIFF 2.2 per kilde → mål-par under `out/`:"
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:5fe2dc64ab",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Deeper reading"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Videre lesning"
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:5fead02492",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "A project pairs a source language with the locales you translate into, the files in scope, and the flows that process them. Naming it is the only required step — everything else is configured visually. The project home shows each content collection's translation status — how many blocks are covered per locale — and lets you extract content into the project store to refresh it."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Et prosjekt parer et kildespråk med språkene du oversetter til, filene i omfang og flytene som behandler dem. Å navngi det er det eneste obligatoriske steget — alt annet konfigureres visuelt. Prosjekthjemmet viser oversettelsesstatusen for hver innholdssamling — hvor mange blokker som er dekket per språk — og lar deg trekke innhold ut i prosjektlageret for å friske den opp."
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:60f18fb94e",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Once you've tried kapi in the browser, install\nthe binary to run it locally against your own files."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Når du har [prøvd kapi i nettleseren](/kapi/get-started/quickstart), installer\nbinærfilen for å kjøre den lokalt mot dine egne filer."
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:61dc823da4",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "1. Plug kapi into Claude"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "1. Koble kapi til Claude"
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:626b030928",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Each returning XLIFF is applied independently. A failure on one\ninput (parse error, missing manifest, stale source) doesn't abort the\nothers — per-file outcomes are reported and the exit code reflects any\nfailure."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Hver returnerende XLIFF behandles uavhengig. En feil på én inndatafil\n(parsefeil, manglende manifest, foreldet kilde) avbryter ikke de andre —\nutfallet rapporteres per fil, og avslutningskoden gjenspeiler enhver feil."
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:62cc423a30",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Both are on by default. --no-tm and --no-tm-update disable them\n(e.g. cold-translation workflows or dry-run review)."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Begge er på som standard. `--no-tm` og `--no-tm-update` slår dem av\n(f.eks. for arbeidsflyter med kald oversettelse eller gjennomgang som tørrkjøring)."
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:66c3e1c2a6",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Windows (amd64, arm64)"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Windows (amd64, arm64)"
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:66cb6599df",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "See Using kapi with Claude for the skill-based\nworkflow, or Using Kapi with AI Assistants for MCP setup with\nClaude Code, Cursor, and Windsurf."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Se [Bruke kapi med Claude](/kapi/get-started/use-with-claude) for den\nferdighetsbaserte arbeidsflyten, eller [Bruke Kapi med AI-assistenter](/reference/mcp)\nfor MCP-oppsett med Claude Code, Cursor og Windsurf."
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:67dad2856a",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "From source (Go developers)"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Fra kildekode (Go-utviklere)"
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:6b0f8dfbfd",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Merge compares every incoming block's <source> against the current\nsource file. If the source text drifted since extract (someone edited\nthe JSON while the XLIFF was out with the translator), that block is\nreported as stale and skipped — neither applied nor TM-absorbed.\nYou can re-extract and re-translate the drifted portion."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Flettingen sammenligner hver innkommende blokks `<source>` med den gjeldende\nkildefilen. Hvis kildeteksten har endret seg siden uttrekket (noen redigerte\nJSON-en mens XLIFF-en var ute hos oversetteren), rapporteres den blokken som\n**foreldet** og **hoppes over** — verken anvendt eller absorbert i\noversettelsesminnet. Du kan trekke ut og oversette den endrede delen på nytt."
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:6bd3579394",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Modes & bindings"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Moduser og bindinger"
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T13:20:27Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T13:20:27Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:6da8f48220",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "The installer is Authenticode-signed and registers a Start-menu entry and uninstaller."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Installasjonsprogrammet er Authenticode-signert og registrerer en\nstartmenyoppføring og et avinstalleringsprogram."
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:6fab445744",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "The output is accented text like ▒ Ĥéļļö, Ŵöŕļđ! ▒ that exposes untranslated\nstrings and layout problems. With no --target-lang, kapi uses the qps\npseudo-locale; pass --target-lang to target a real locale."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Utdataene er aksenttekst som `▒ Ĥéļļö, Ŵöŕļđ! ▒` som avslører uoversatte\nstrenger og layoutproblemer. Uten `--target-lang` bruker kapi pseudospråkkoden\n`qps`; send `--target-lang` for å sikte på en ekte språkkode."
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:70e204899f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "The tour above shows each surface in motion; here is the path through them when\nyou start from nothing. Everything is configured visually — there is no YAML to\nwrite by hand."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Omvisningen over viser hver flate i bevegelse; her er veien gjennom dem når du\nstarter fra ingenting. Alt konfigureres visuelt — det er ingen YAML å skrive for\nhånd."
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:7102842054",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Desktop app"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Skrivebordsapp"
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:7139513c4d",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Estimate translation volume for cost planning:"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Anslå oversettelsesvolum for kostnadsplanlegging:"
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:71c7cb4b92",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "How kapi exchanges content with external TMS and CAT tools through standard bilingual formats — extract to XLIFF or PO, translate anywhere, and merge back byte-exactly while keeping translation memory and terminology in the loop."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Hvordan kapi utveksler innhold med eksterne TMS- og CAT-verktøy gjennom standard tospråklige formater — trekk ut til XLIFF eller PO, oversett hvor som helst, og flett tilbake byte-eksakt med oversettelsesminne og terminologi i sløyfen."
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T13:20:27Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T13:20:27Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:72735da49a",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Day 2: translator work"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Dag 2: oversetterarbeid"
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:72867b93e1",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Score a draft against a profile. --min-score makes it a CI gate — kapi exits\nnon-zero when the score is below the threshold:"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Vurder et utkast mot en profil. `--min-score` gjør det til en CI-port — kapi\navslutter med ikke-null når poengsummen er under terskelen:"
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:729fb24c87",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Installation — all platforms and options"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "[Installering](/kapi/get-started/installation) — alle plattformer og alternativer"
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:72c22051ab",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Stdout summarizes:"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Stdout oppsummerer:"
          }
        ]
      },
