          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:89ea57b838",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "There are two ways to drive Kapi:"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Det er to måter å bruke Kapi på:"
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:8a2dedc120",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "If your strings live in a known stack's i18n catalogs, skip the manual add and\nlet kapi init --framework <stack> (for example react-i18next, nextjs,\nflutter) pre-fill the content mapping for you — see\nkapi presets list --framework."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Hvis strengene dine ligger i i18n-katalogene til en kjent teknologistabel, hopp\nover den manuelle `add`-en og la `kapi init --framework <stack>` (for eksempel\n`react-i18next`, `nextjs`, `flutter`) forhåndsutfylle innholdskartleggingen for\ndeg — se `kapi presets list --framework`."
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:8a62524ae5",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "The .kapi recipe"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": ".kapi-oppskriften"
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:8aebb21122",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Manage terminology"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
