    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:c3fffb8a9f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "A quick tour"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "En rask omvisning"
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:c415755ac2",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "TM pre-fill on extract — every segment is looked up against the\n  project TM before it lands in the XLIFF. Exact matches are pre-filled\n  with state=\"translated\"; fuzzy matches above the recipe's\n  tm.fuzzy_threshold are pre-filled as fuzzy. The translator's CAT\n  tool shows leverage as a normal TM match."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "**TM-forhåndsutfylling ved uttrekk** — hvert segment slås opp mot prosjektets\n  oversettelsesminne før det lander i XLIFF-en. Eksakte treff forhåndsutfylles\n  med `state=\"translated\"`; fuzzy-treff over oppskriftens `tm.fuzzy_threshold`\n  forhåndsutfylles som fuzzy. Oversetterens CAT-verktøy viser gjenbruket som et\n  vanlig TM-treff."
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:c46cf2ff1b",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": ":::note\nPO output is one entry per block (matches the segmentation-off case).\nEnabling defaults.segmentation.source: true together with\n--format po errors early; emit XLIFF for projects that rely on\nsentence-level segmentation.\n:::"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": ":::note\nPO-utdata er én oppføring per blokk (tilsvarer tilfellet med segmentering av).\nÅ slå på `defaults.segmentation.source: true` sammen med `--format po` feiler\ntidlig; skriv ut XLIFF for prosjekter som er avhengige av segmentering på\nsetningsnivå.\n:::"
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:c47990fff3",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Everything you configure is written to a portable <name>.kapi recipe file.\nCommit it to git to share with your team, reopen it in Kapi Desktop, or run it\nfrom the command line:"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Alt du konfigurerer skrives til en portabel `<name>.kapi`-oppskriftsfil. Sjekk\nden inn i git for å dele med laget ditt, gjenåpne den i Kapi Desktop, eller kjør\nden fra kommandolinjen:"
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:c6681bd1a4",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "This page walks the smallest end-to-end loop: init → read the recipe → run a\nflow → merge the files out."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Denne siden går gjennom den minste ende-til-ende-sløyfen: `init` → les\noppskriften → kjør en flyt → `merge` filene ut."
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:c7110b045a",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "A file-level <note category=\"kapi\"> on each XLIFF stamping the\n  batch id, source file, and source hash"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "En `<note category=\"kapi\">` på filnivå i hver XLIFF som stempler batch-id,\n  kildefil og kildehash"
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:c880fe3c51",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Kapi Desktop"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Kapi Desktop"
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:cc05f5d58e",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Lists every TM entry written or updated by a specific merge with\ntimestamp, source file path, block content hash, and originating\nXLIFF filename — the answer to \"what did this merge do?\" without\nleaving the CLI."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Lister hver TM-oppføring skrevet eller oppdatert av en bestemt fletting, med\ntidsstempel, kildefilsti, blokkens innholdshash og opprinnelig XLIFF-filnavn —\nsvaret på «hva gjorde denne flettingen?» uten å forlate CLI-en."
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:ccaf5c2214",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Set up a .kapi project with kapi init — capture languages, content globs, and flows once, then run flows and merge files without repeating flags. The recommended day-to-day working model."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Sett opp et .kapi-prosjekt med kapi init — fang språk, innholdsmønstre og flyter én gang, og kjør deretter flyter og flett filer uten å gjenta flagg. Den anbefalte arbeidsmodellen for daglig bruk."
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T13:20:27Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T13:20:27Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:cd1aace34e",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "For a full interactive terminal, open the CLI Playground."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "For en fullverdig interaktiv terminal, åpne [CLI-lekeplassen](/playground-cli)."
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:cd921ad3fc",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Modes & bindings — how ad-hoc and project runs differ, and when\n  to mix them."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "[Moduser og bindinger](/kapi/modes) — hvordan ad hoc- og prosjektkjøringer\n  skiller seg, og når du bør kombinere dem."
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:cda6875310",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Download and run the signed installer from GitHub Releases:"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Last ned og kjør det signerte installasjonsprogrammet fra\n[GitHub Releases](https://github.com/neokapi/neokapi/releases):"
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:cef07f2092",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Ad-hoc = the file binding — you name -i/-o."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "**Ad hoc** = `file`-bindingen — du angir `-i`/`-o`."
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:d2af1382b3",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Extraction bookkeeping (the captured skeletons and a manifest) recorded\n  in the project's gitignored cache so kapi merge can reattach the\n  returned translations and rebuild the source byte-for-byte — for document\n  and markup formats and for keyed catalog formats alike (JSON, YAML,\n  .properties, Android XML, .resx, Apple\n  .strings/.stringsdict/.xcstrings, .arb, i18next, design tokens)"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Uttrekksbokføring (de fangede skjelettene og et manifest) lagret i prosjektets\n  gitignorerte hurtigbuffer slik at `kapi merge` kan feste de returnerte\n  oversettelsene igjen og gjenoppbygge kilden byte for byte — for dokument- og\n  markupformater så vel som for nøkkelbaserte katalogformater (JSON, YAML,\n  `.properties`, Android XML, `.resx`, Apple\n  `.strings`/`.stringsdict`/`.xcstrings`, `.arb`, i18next, designtokener)"
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:d2b577650f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "1. Initialize the project"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "1. Initialiser prosjektet"
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:d305b3bdc0",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Kapi runs the same commands two ways — the only difference is whether state is kept:"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Kapi kjører de **samme kommandoene** på to måter — den eneste forskjellen er om tilstand beholdes:"
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:d38dcf5ccb",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Verify the install"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Verifiser installasjonen"
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:d391ab972e",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Create your first project — kapi init,\n  read the recipe, run a flow, merge the files out."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "[Opprett ditt første prosjekt](/kapi/get-started/first-project) — `kapi init`,\n  les oppskriften, kjør en flyt, flett ut filene."
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:d393790ae9",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "From anywhere inside the project tree, run a flow by name:"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Fra hvor som helst i prosjekttreet, kjør en flyt ved navn:"
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:d4b1ea5708",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Overview"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Oversikt"
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T13:20:27Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T13:20:27Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:d564e2807f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "See the round-trip on a bilingual file"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Se rundturen på en tospråklig fil"
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:d58aa9b677",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Do ad-hoc and project mode mix?"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Kan ad hoc og prosjektmodus kombineres?"
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:d5a50aab97",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Ad-hoc: loose files"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Ad hoc: løse filer"
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:d664282e62",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Recipes"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Oppskrifter"
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:d861ce722d",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "A project's content is the set of files it translates. Glob patterns are grouped into named collections — documentation, store UI, contracts, templates — each mapping source files to their translated counterparts. The Content view shows the patterns alongside the real files they match and the format Kapi detected for each."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Et prosjekts innhold er settet av filer det oversetter. Globmønstre grupperes i navngitte samlinger — dokumentasjon, butikkgrensesnitt, kontrakter, maler — som hver kartlegger kildefiler til sine oversatte motstykker. Innholdsvisningen viser mønstrene side om side med de virkelige filene de treffer og formatet Kapi oppdaget for hver av dem."
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:d87665fc93",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "**amd64**: `kapi-desktop-X.Y.Z-windows-amd64-setup.exe`"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "**amd64**: `kapi-desktop-X.Y.Z-windows-amd64-setup.exe`"
          }
        ]
      },
