    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:f81fa41821",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Because both front-ends run the same engine, a workflow built in one works in\nthe other: the flows and the project file are identical."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Siden begge grensesnittene kjører samme motor, fungerer en arbeidsflyt bygget\ni det ene også i det andre: flytene og prosjektfilen er identiske."
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:f9800c00f2",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "PO output carries kapi's bookkeeping as extracted comments:"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "PO-utdata bærer kapis bokføring som uttrukne kommentarer:"
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:fb5a2dcdc6",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "The two sections below cover each. If you only want the command line, you need\nthe first section alone."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "De to seksjonene under dekker hver av dem. Vil du bare ha kommandolinjen,\ntrenger du kun den første seksjonen."
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb:fbb864c714",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Five starter packs ship built in: `professional-b2b`, `friendly-dtc`,\n`technical-docs`, `marketing-blog`, and `customer-support`. See\n[Brand Voice](/framework/checks/brand-voice)."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Fem startpakker følger med innebygd: `professional-b2b`, `friendly-dtc`,\n`technical-docs`, `marketing-blog` og `customer-support`. Se\n[Merkevarestemme](/framework/checks/brand-voice)."
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
